quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,94,Futhi ningabokwenza izifungo zenu phakathi kwenu ukuthi zibe inkohliso kunjengokushelela konyawo emva kokuqiniseka kwalo futhi yizwani okubi ngenxa yokuthi nanivimbela abantu endleleni kaMvelinqangi futhi okwenu kuyoba isijeziso esikhulu (esinzima)
  16,95,Futhi ningabothenga isivumelwano sikaMvelinqangi ngenani elincane (ngokungeyinzuzo yalutho) kuphela okukuMvelinqangi kungcono kunina ukuba nje benazi
  16,96,"Konke lokho eninako kuyedlula kepha konke lokhu okukuMvelinqangi kuhlala kukhona njalo futhi ngempela siyobanika umvuzo labo ababekezelayo, umvuzo wabo ngenxa yobuhle ababekwenza"
  16,97,"Lowo owenza izenzo ezilungileyo ngisho noma ngabe owesilisa noma owesifazane ebe engakholwa ngakho-ke siyomenza ukuthi aphile impilo enhle futhi ngempela siyobanika umvuzo, umvuzo wabo ngenxa yobuhle ababekwenza"
  16,98,Ngakho-ke uma ufunda iQur’an funa isiphephelo kuMvelinqangi ukuze uphephe kusathane owagxoshwa (embusweni kaMvelinqangi)
  16,99,Ngempela yena (usathane) akanalo igunya phezu kwalabo abakholwayo futhi babeka ithemba eNkosini yabo
  16,100,Kuphela igunya lakhe liphezu kwalabo abangabangane bakhe kanye nakulabo abenzela uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni (abakhonzi bezithixo)
  16,101,Futhi uma sishintsha ivesi endaweni yevesi manjalo uMvelinqangi owazi ngokwedlulele ngalokho akwembulayo (akuthumela phansi) bathi “kuphela wena ungumqambi” (wamanga) kepha iningi labo alazi
  16,102,"Ithi, “umoya ongcwele (uGabriyeli) oyilethile (iQur’an) evela eNkosini yakho ngeqiniso ukuze iqinise labo abakholwayo, nokubahola futhi ibe njengomlethi wezindaba ezimnandi kwabakholwayo”"